<div class='humble-topic-header'>Caching</div>

Though optional, it is highly recommended that you utilize a memcache instance with Humble.  Humble will store frequently accessed resources in Memcache, otherwise those resources
will be retrieved from the MySQL DB, which has unnecessary overhead for static resources.<br />
<br />
